title: Spyder Auto Installation: 2004-2013 Chevrolet Colorado/GMC Canyon Projector Headlights
description: This video demonstrates how to install a set of Spyder Auto projector headlights on any 2004 through 2013 model year Chevrolet Colorado or GMC Canyon models. This complete walkthrough covers the install from start to finish and includes helpful tips throughout to facilitate a successful installation.
